Terms and Conditions for Registering an Account Welcome to the Philippines TRC Inc. System! By registering an account, you agree to the following terms and conditions. Please read them carefully before proceeding.
1. Eligibility 1.1. You must be an authorized employee, contractor, or partner of Philippines TRC Inc. to register for an account. 1.2. You must provide accurate and up-to-date information during registration.
2. Account Security 2.1. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your username and password. 2.2. Sharing account credentials with others is strictly prohibited. 2.3. Notify the system administrator immediately if you suspect unauthorized access to your account.
3. Use of the System 3.1. You agree to use the system solely for authorized and lawful purposes related to your work or partnership with Philippines TRC Inc. 3.2. Unauthorized access, misuse, or tampering with the system is prohibited and may result in disciplinary or legal action. 3.3. The system may only be used in compliance with applicable laws and company policies.
4. Data Privacy 4.1. The information you provide will be handled in accordance with the Philippines TRC Inc. Privacy Policy. 4.2. You consent to the collection, processing, and use of your data as required for account creation and system functionality.
5. Intellectual Property 5.1. All content, materials, and resources within the system are the property of Philippines TRC Inc. 5.2. Copying, distributing, or modifying system content without prior authorization is prohibited.
6. Monitoring and Audit 6.1. Philippines TRC Inc. reserves the right to monitor and log activities within the system for security and compliance purposes. 6.2. Misuse of the system may result in account suspension or termination.
7. Termination of Account 7.1. Philippines TRC Inc. reserves the right to terminate or suspend accounts that violate these terms. 7.2. Terminated accounts will lose access to system resources immediately.
8. Updates to Terms 8.1. Philippines TRC Inc. reserves the right to update these terms at any time. 8.2. Continued use of the system after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
9. Limitation of Liability Philippines TRC Inc. will not be liable for any loss or damage resulting from unauthorized access or use of your account.
10. Acceptance By registering an account, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these terms and conditions.
